'''''Agony of Christ''''' ni film yo muri [[Gana]] yo muri 2009 iyobowe na Frank Rajah Arase<ref>https://www.nollywoodreinvented.com/2012/11/agony-of-christ.html</ref> . akaba ari film yamenyekanye cyane kuko iganisha ku kwizera kwa muntu kuko igaragaza Umwuka wera ndetse n'umwuka wa sekibi imbaraga  hagati y'umupadiri  ndetse n'abapfumu hakabikorera ku musore umwe uba utazi icyo gukora <ref>https://www.naijapals.com/nigerian-movies/Agony_of_the_Christ</ref>. 

== Umugambi ==
Umusore yahunze umudugudu we kuko umupadiri gakondo yashakaga ko yicwa<ref>https://myhealthbasics.site/nadia-buari-a-top-movie-celebrity-in-ghana/</ref>. Yakijijwe nabakristo bamutoje ubumenyi bw'ubukristo aravuka ubwa kabiri<ref>https://www.modernghana.com/entertainment/7985/agony-of-the-christ-premiered.html</ref>. Yagarutse mu mudugudu we aho basengaga imana nto<ref>https://hyperleap.com/topic/Agony_of_Christ_(film)</ref>. Igikorwa cye cyo guhindura abantu bose bo mu mudugudu kuba umukirisitu cyaburijwemo n’umupadiri w’igihugu<ref>https://frankensaurus.com/Agony_of_Christ_(film)</ref>, wemera ko ibyo bibaho bityo amushora mu ntambara yo mu mwuka<ref>https://www.nairaland.com/726922/anybody-watched-agony-christ</ref>. 

